@startuml
state InitialState
state CardInserted
state PINEntry
state PINVerified
state OptionsDisplayed
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state CashDispensed
state ReceiptPrinting
state CardReturned
state Resetting

InitialState --> CardInserted: Insert Card [*]

CardInserted --> PINEntry: Enter PIN

PINEntry --> PINVerified: Verify PIN

PINVerified --> OptionsDisplayed: Provide options

OptionsDisplayed --> ProcessingWithdrawal: Select withdrawal

ProcessingWithdrawal --> CashDispensed: Process withdrawal

CashDispensed --> ReceiptPrinting: Print receipt

ReceiptPrinting --> CardReturned: Return card

CardReturned --> Resetting: Brief moment

Resetting --> InitialState: Reset
@enduml
